<div id="sec1" class="blurb">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      
      <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
				<div class="panel panel-default">
					<div class="panel-heading text-center custom-heading"><h3>What we offer you</h3></div>
					<div class="panel-body">
						<ul class="lead-text">
							<li>Enjoy a unique environment that will motivate you to solve more problems than ever before.</li>
							<li>Draw from a rich database of interesting physics problems.</li>
							<li>Take part in competitions against other phykings to raise your level and win gold.</li>
							<li>Contribute with your own problems and solutions and get rewards.</li>
							<li>Learn from your peers' solutions and improve your problem solving skills.</li>
							<li>Become a real phyking in a growing community of phykings.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
